elements.name: quantity
elements.description:
Total number of units, associated with the HTS Number that corresponds to UOM Code.

Two decimal places are implied. Space fill if quantity not required/does not apply.

elements.name: unitOfMeasureCode
elements.description:
A unit of measure code that corresponds to the Quantity as prescribed by the HTS Number reported.

The unit of measure must match exactly the unit of measure as listed in the Harmonized Tariff Schedule for the tariff number.
